node.accessibility_caption:
BACK-TO-SCHOOL GIVEAWAY ✨

It’s back to school time, so I partnered with @onceuponafarm to give TWO WINNERS a 24-pack of pouches + $100 gift card to #target 🎯

Alright parents, time to prep those fridges for back-to-school 👏🏼🛒 The perfect lunchbox addition comes from @onceuponafarm! Refrigerated fruit 🫐🍌and vegetable blends 🥬 that are organic, cold-pressed that have no added sugars, colors and preservatives - it's just simple, real, nutrient-rich snacks that are super convenient for Mom and the perfect lunchbox addition for the kiddos 😋✨

Little one not in school yet? Snack time is Gianna's favorite time of the day and our go-to? Once Upon A Farm. She absolutely loves Green Kale & Apples 🍎 Head to the refrigerated aisle of your local @target store or add to your next drive-up or pick-up order!

node.accessibility_caption:
What does your day-to-day routine look like? Getting back to a routine can be refreshing and a great way to restart, whether it's the hectic back to school schedule or just starting a new routine, @grovecollaborative's best-sellers from Grove Co. are available at Target, in stores and online! Grove Co. products offer uncompromised performance that are great for your family and the planet. Using aluminum bottles and reusable glass containers, their products use 100% natural fragrance!

Find Grove Co. at your local @target or visit online at target.com to keep your routine refreshed. Target Circle members will get 10% off their purchase through the end of August. // #grovepartner #TargetXGroveCo

node.accessibility_caption:
G I V E A W A Y

I have partnered with @forgereads to give FIVE WINNERS a copy of their newest novels 📚✨

I just finished my @target run and picked up two books that looked too good, I couldn't resist 😆 I snagged She Wouldn't Change A Thing by Sarah Adlakha and I Don't Forgive You by Aggie Blum Thompson! Let me tell you a little more about these books:

She Wouldn't Change A Thing by Sarah Adlakha. Maria Forssman wakes up in her seventeen year old body, she doesn't know how she got there. All she knows is that in a few weeks tragedy will strike her husband that will lead them to meeting. Would you change fate - even if it means losing what you love?

I Don't Forgive You by Aggie Blum Thompson. Allie Ross is an accomplished photographer and devoted mother of an adorable little boy. Allie Ross just moved to an upscale DC suburb, the kind of place where parenting feels like a competitive sport. She's desperate to make a good first impression...then, she's framed for murder.

If you need a good novel, head to your local @target store and grab the newest novels from @forgereads 📚🎯

TO ENTER:

📖 Like this post
📖 Follow @forgereads 
📖 Tag a fellow book reader & let them know which novel your excited for (1 tag = 1 entry, unlimited)
